{
  "info": {
    "name": "N8N Basic API",
    "_postman_id": "f79a5f5d-4a2f-4df8-8e12-4a61d450f2f0",
    "description": "# N8N Basic API\n\nImportera denna collection i Postman för att testa samtliga webhook-endpoints i `n8n/workflows/n8n-basic`.\n\n## Upplägg\n\n- **Grunder**: webhook-intag och enkel routing\n- **Lead och CRM**: kvalificering, routing, Twenty\n- **Support och AI**: Flowise, Chatwoot, omvägar\n\n## Variabler\n\n- `baseUrl` = `http://localhost:5678`\n- `n8nUser` = `admin`\n- `n8nPass` = `admin`\n\n> Flöde 01 (manuell trigger) har ingen webhook och testas därför inte via Postman.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "basic",
    "basic": [
      {
        "key": "username",
        "value": "{{n8nUser}}",
        "type": "string"
      },
      {
        "key": "password",
        "value": "{{n8nPass}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:5678"
    },
    {
      "key": "n8nUser",
      "value": "admin"
    },
    {
      "key": "n8nPass",
      "value": "admin"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "01-03 Grunder",
      "description": "Grundläggande webhook-testning för N8N Basic 02 och 03.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "02 - basic intake",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Maja\",\n  \"email\": \"maja@example.com\",\n  \"message\": \"Hej! Jag vill veta mer.\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/webhook/basic-intake",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "webhook",
                "basic-intake"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Tar emot enkel JSON och svarar med normaliserad payload.\n\nKopplad till: `N8N Basic 02 - Webhook, normalisering och svar.json`"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "03 - basic routing",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Ali\",\n  \"message\": \"Jag har problem med min leverans.\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/webhook/basic-routing",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "webhook",
                "basic-routing"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Routar till support, sälj eller allmän kö beroende på meddelandetext.\n\nKopplad till: `N8N Basic 03 - Webhook med enkel routing.json`"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
